	(7954,2542,'_mcb-products','<h3></h3>\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Full_Sail_AMBER_75_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2521\" alt=\"Full_Sail_AMBER_75_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Full_Sail_AMBER_75_165.png\" width=\"75\" height=\"165\" /></a>Full Sail Amber Ale</h3>\r\n<h5><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;\"><strong>ABV 6%</strong></span></h5>\r\n<h5><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;\">Malty Sweet, Reddish Amber Hue &amp; a Spicy Floral Hop Finish</span></h5>\r\nOur Amber is a sweet, malty, medium-bodied ale with a spicy, floral hop finish. It’s brewed with 2-row Pale, Crystal and Chocolate malts. And we hop it with Mt. Hoods and Cascades. We’re as proud of it today as we were back in ’89. And over the years it’s earned 16 Gold Medals. Not that we’re keeping track or anything.'),
