	(8206,2148,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/bud_light_lime_btl_CLEAR_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2416\" alt=\"bud_light_lime_btl_CLEAR_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/bud_light_lime_btl_CLEAR_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Light Lime</h3>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.2%</h5>\r\nBud Light Lime is a premium light beer that combines all the drinkability of Bud Light with the taste of fresh squeezed lime.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Landshark_Lager_clear_101x362_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2638\" alt=\"Landshark_Lager_clear_101x362_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Landshark_Lager_clear_101x362_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Landshark</h3>\r\n<h5>ISLAND STYLE LAGER</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.7%</h5>\r\nA refreshing, drinkable island style lager brewed with a complex blend of hop varieties giving the beer a distinctive hop note taste.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n\r\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich-Ultra-Lime-Cactus_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2425\" alt=\"Mich-Ultra-Lime-Cactus_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich-Ultra-Lime-Cactus_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a></span>\r\n<h3>Michelob Ultra Lime Cactus</h3>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4%</h5>\r\nMichelob ULTRA Lime Cactus: a squeeze of fresh lime with a southwestern twist. This fruit-infused light pilsner wets the palate with a hint of a natural lime, while floral undertones derived from the cactus offer deep refreshment.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich-Ultra-Pom-Ras_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2424\" alt=\"Mich-Ultra-Pom-Ras_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich-Ultra-Pom-Ras_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Michelob Ultra Pomegranate Raspberry</h3>\r\n<h5>RIPE FOR ENJOYMENT ANYTIME</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4%</h5>\r\nThis pilsner fuses berry aroma, raspberry flavor and a hint of pomegranate for crisp refreshment.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Redbridge_clear_small_47_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2639\" alt=\"Redbridge_clear_small_47_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Redbridge_clear_small_47_165.png\" width=\"47\" height=\"165\" /></a>Redbridge</h3>\r\n<h5>GLUTEN-FREE BEER</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.5%</h5>\r\nRed Bridge is brewed without any barley, employing sorghum as a source of fermentable sugars for the real beer taste without any gluten.\r\n\r\nBeautiful amber color with rich aroma notes of grain and a captivating citrus hop bouquet. The taste is slightly sweet and drying, balanced by the superb hop finish.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/wb-bottle.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2637\" alt=\"wb bottle\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/wb-bottle.jpg\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Wild Blue</h3>\r\n<h5>ABV:8%</h5>\r\nWild Blue is a blueberry lager that fuses the juice of nature’s perfect fruit – blueberries – with premium American and German hops, two row and six-row barley malt and cereal grains. Wild Blue has a full taste with a pleasant blueberry aroma and flavor.\r\n\r\nIts fun, irreverent spirit is conveyed in every aspect of the beer, from the bottle label that features a bulldog kicking a blueberry to its full-bodied taste. Wild Blue is the perfect drink for adults who are thirsting for something new.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/BL-Chelada_71_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2414\" alt=\"BL-Chelada_71_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/BL-Chelada_71_165.png\" width=\"71\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Light Chelada</h3>\r\n<h5>SPICE UP YOUR BEER</h5>\r\n<h5>YEAR ROUND</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.2%</h5>\r\nBud Light &amp; Clamato Chelada honor that tradition by combining Anheuser-Buschâ€™s classic American-style lagers with the spicy, invigorating taste of Clamato Tomato Cocktail, made by Cadbury Schweppes Americas Beverages (CSAB).'),
