	(8166,2549,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Bud_Light_spring_13_btl_100x_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2412\" alt=\"Bud_Light_spring_13_btl_100x_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Bud_Light_spring_13_btl_100x_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Light</h3>\r\n<h5>AMERICAN STYLE LIGHT LAGER</h5>\r\n<h5>YEAR ROUND</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.2%</h5>\r\nSince 1982, Bud Light has grown to become the best-selling beer in the United States and the No. 1 light beer in the world. Brewed with all natural ingredients and a blend of two and six-row barley malt, Bud Light’s characteristics of a clean aroma and a crisp smooth taste is a guarantee for beer drinkers. The sure sign of a good time.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/platinum_44_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2417\" alt=\"platinum_44_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/platinum_44_165.png\" width=\"44\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Light Platinum</h3>\r\n<h5>TRIPLE-FILTERED LIGHT BEER</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 6%</h5>\r\nThis unique 6% ABV, triple-filtered light beer delivers the smooth taste consumers love in an eye-catching cobalt blue bottle.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/bud_light_lime_btl_CLEAR_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2416\" alt=\"bud_light_lime_btl_CLEAR_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/bud_light_lime_btl_CLEAR_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Light Lime</h3>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.2%</h5>\r\nBud Light Lime is a premium light beer that combines all the drinkability of Bud Light with the taste of fresh squeezed lime.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/BL-Lime-a-rita_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2415\" alt=\"BL-Lime-a-rita_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/BL-Lime-a-rita_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Light Lime-A-Rita</h3>\r\n<h5>ABV: 8%</h5>\r\nThis bold new Margarita with a Twist is 8% ABV and perfectly balanced to deliver authentic margarita flavor and a delightfully refreshing finish. Versions with both 6 percent and 8 percent alcohol by volume.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3> </h3>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/bl-strawberita.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2413\" alt=\"bl strawberita\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/bl-strawberita.jpg\" width=\"68\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Light Straw-ber-Rita</h3>\r\n<h5>FLAVORED MALT BEVERAGE</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 6.0%</h5>\r\nA margarita with a twist. This is a strawberry version of the popular Bud Light Lime Lime-A-Rita.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/BL-Chelada_71_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2414\" alt=\"BL-Chelada_71_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/BL-Chelada_71_165.png\" width=\"71\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Light Chelada</h3>\r\n<h5>SPICE UP YOUR BEER</h5>\r\n<h5>YEAR ROUND</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.2%</h5>\r\nBudweiser &amp; Clamato Chelada and Bud Light &amp; Clamato Chelada honor that tradition by combining Anheuser-Buschâ€™s classic American-style lagers with the spicy, invigorating taste of Clamato Tomato Cocktail, made by Cadbury Schweppes Americas Beverages (CSAB).\r\n<div> </div>'),
	(8132,2550,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Budweiser_-_KOB_70x_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2366\" alt=\"Budweiser_-_KOB_70x_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Budweiser_-_KOB_70x_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Budweiser</h3>\r\n<h4>The King of Beers</h4>\r\n<h4>ABV: 5%</h4>\r\nGolden color with subtle aroma notes of malt and noble hops, along with trace citrus and fruity notes. The taste is crisp and clean with a wonderful finish.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Bud_Black_Crown_btl_clear_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2367\" alt=\"Bud_Black_Crown_btl_clear_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Bud_Black_Crown_btl_clear_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Budweiser Black Crown</h3>\r\n<h5>Golden Amber Lager</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 6%</h5>\r\nA new 6% ABV golden amber lager from Budweiser that is distinctively flavorful, yet smooth and drinkable.Black Crown is brewed with toasted caramel malt and finished over beechwood chips for a distinctively smooth, flavorful finish.  Brewed using Budweiser’s 1876 yeast strain and signature aging process.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Budweiser_SELECT_100x360_clr_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2369\" alt=\"Budweiser_SELECT_100x360_clr_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Budweiser_SELECT_100x360_clr_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Budweiser SELECT</h3>\r\n<h4>99 Calories</h4>\r\n<h4>ABV: 4.3%</h4>\r\nBudweiser Select delivers it all - a bold taste, full-flavor and a clean finish, it\'s the best of both worlds. This full flavored, low calorie beer has a slightly dark, golden color with aromas of toasted grains and Bavarian hops. Subtle malty taste notes carry through to a crisp,clean hop finish.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Bud_Select_55_CLEAR_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2370\" alt=\"Bud_Select_55_CLEAR_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Bud_Select_55_CLEAR_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Budweiser SELECT 55</h3>\r\n<h5>\"The world\'s lightest beer!\"</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 2.4%</h5>\r\nSelect 55 is brewed with specialty malts and a blend of imported and domestic hopping. This beer has a light golden color and offers aroma notes of toasted malt and subtle hopping.\r\n\r\nSelect 55 is the lightest beer in the world with fewer calories than any other beer option currently available. Per 12-ounce serving, Select 55 has 55 calories and 1.9 grams of carbs.\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/proj12-bottle.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2581\" alt=\"proj12 bottle\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/proj12-bottle.jpg\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Project 12</h3>\r\nProject 12 started when Budweiser’s 12 brewmasters across America were asked to write a unique beer recipe worthy of the Budweiser name. The sampler pack includes: A <strong>deep-amber lager</strong> with 6 percent alcohol by volume (ABV),  A <strong>deep-golden pilsner</strong> with 6 percent ABV, and A <strong>bourbon cask lager</strong> with 5.5 percent ABV.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Bud_Ice_clear_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2368\" alt=\"Bud_Ice_clear_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Bud_Ice_clear_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Bud Ice</h3>\r\n<h4>Cold-Filtered</h4>\r\n<h4>ABV: 5.5%</h4>\r\nIntroduced nationally in 1995, Bud Ice is American\'s first draft beer to be ice brewed. Anheuser-Busch\'s exclusive ice-brewing process takes the beer to a temperature below freezing, leading to the formation of ice crystals. The beer then rests in storage at 28 degrees Fahrenheit for several days before being cold-filtered and packaged, resulting in a rich, smooth draft taste that is remarkably easy to drink. Bud Ice Light is a light alternative to this ice-brewed beverage.'),
