	(6958,2252,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Black-Tan-12oz-NR.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2465\" alt=\"Black &amp; Tan 12oz NR\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Black-Tan-12oz-NR.jpg\" width=\"49\" height=\"165\" /></a>Yuengling Black and Tan</h3>\r\nYuengling Original Black &amp; Tan is a pioneer brand that models a traditional\r\nEnglish Half &amp; Half. Introduced in 1986, Yuengling produced one of the\r\nfirst hand-crafted draft blends to lead this style of American brewing.It has a faint sweetness\r\nwith hints of caramel and coffee from the dark roasted malts. One sip and\r\nyou’ll appreciate how Yuengling raised the bar with our Original Black &amp; Tan.'),
