	(7026,2246,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Porter-12oz-NR.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2469\" alt=\"Porter 12oz NR\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Porter-12oz-NR.jpg\" width=\"49\" height=\"165\" /></a>Yuengling Porter</h3>\r\nAn authentic craftstyle beer, our Porter calls for a generous portion of caramel and dark roasted malts, which deliver a rich full-bodied flavor and creamy taste with slight tones of chocolate evident in every sip. It pours dark, topped with a thick foamy head, and imparts a faint malty aroma. This smooth and robust Porter has a unique character that complements any meal from steak or seafood to chocolate desserts. Yuengling Dark Brewed Porter is enjoyed by even the most discerning consumer for its flawless taste and unwavering quality.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
	(8189,2548,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/ultra_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2418\" alt=\"ultra_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/ultra_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Michelob Ultra</h3>\r\n<h5>LIVE LIFE TO THE ULTRA</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.2%</h5>\r\nLess is truly more. Light golden in color with light notes of citrus, this low-carb, American-style light lager is made from two-row Munich malts and European select hops for a clean, refreshing body and finish.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich_Lager_clear_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2421\" alt=\"Mich_Lager_clear_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich_Lager_clear_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Michelob Lager</h3>\r\n<h5>THE SAME, PERFECT SINCE 1896</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 5%| IBUS: 18</h5>\r\n<h5><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;\">Michelob Original Lager is a malty, full-bodied European-style premium lager. From its inception to today, it stands out as a distinctive, high-quality beer for connoisseurs.</span></h5>\r\nThis Original Lager is brewed traditionally, using European noble aroma hop varieties and a 100-percent-malt blend of the finest two-row and caramel malts. It is fermented and aged with Anheuser-Busch’s classic lager yeast strain, and cold-matured for balanced crispness.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich_Light_sm_clear_45_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2420\" alt=\"Mich_Light_sm_clear_45_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich_Light_sm_clear_45_165.png\" width=\"45\" height=\"165\" /></a>Michelob Light</h3>\r\n<h5>A LIGHTER TAKE ON THE PREMIUM AMERICAN CLASSIC</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.2%| IBUS: 19</h5>\r\n<h5><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;\">Michelob Light is a full-flavored, rich-tasting light lager with surprisingly low calories and carbohydrate content. Traditionally brewed with European hops and a blend of the finest two-row and caramel malts, Michelob Light is fermented and aged with Anheuser-Busch’s classic lager yeast strain and cold-matured for balanced crispness.</span></h5>\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich_Amber_Bock_clear_48_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2419\" alt=\"Mich_Amber_Bock_clear_48_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich_Amber_Bock_clear_48_165.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"165\" /></a>Michelob AmberBock</h3>\r\n<h5>SPECIALTY MALTS MAKE IT NOTICEABLY SMOOTH</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 5.2%| IBUS: 19</h5>\r\n<h5><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;\">Smoothness, deep-dark color and a roasted malt taste that finishes clean are the hallmarks of this distinctive brew.</span></h5>\r\nBrewed using 100-percent malt â€“ including dark-roasted black and caramel malts and all-imported hops â€“ Michelob AmberBock has a unique, rich amber color and smooth, full-bodied taste.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich-Ultra-Lime-Cactus_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2425\" alt=\"Mich-Ultra-Lime-Cactus_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich-Ultra-Lime-Cactus_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Michelob Ultra Lime Cactus</h3>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4%</h5>\r\nMichelob ULTRA Lime Cactus: a squeeze of fresh lime with a southwestern twist. This fruit-infused light pilsner wets the palate with a hint of a natural lime, while floral undertones derived from the cactus offer deep refreshment.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich-Ultra-Pom-Ras_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2424\" alt=\"Mich-Ultra-Pom-Ras_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich-Ultra-Pom-Ras_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Michelob Ultra Pomegranate Raspberry</h3>\r\n<h5>RIPE FOR ENJOYMENT ANYTIME</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4%</h5>\r\nThis pilsner fuses berry aroma, raspberry flavor and a hint of pomegranate for crisp refreshment.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich_ULTRA_Light_Cider_90x_46_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2423\" alt=\"Mich_ULTRA_Light_Cider_90x_46_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mich_ULTRA_Light_Cider_90x_46_165.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"165\" /></a>Michelob Ultra Light Cider</h3>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4%</h5>\r\nMichelob ULTRA Light Cider is a light, all-natural cider made from crisp apples making it light, refreshing and slightly sweet. Michelob ULTRA Light Cider contains 118 calories per 12 oz serving, and because it’s made from fermented apples, it’s gluten-free.'),
