	(5975,2305,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/heineken-dark-bottle.bmp\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2480\" alt=\"heineken dark bottle\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/heineken-dark-bottle.bmp\" /></a>Heineken Dark</h4>\r\n<h5>ABV:5.1%</h5>\r\nKnown as the dark beer that isn’t, Heineken Special Dark has a smooth refreshing taste that’s light enough to enjoy anytime. The flavor is robust with a hint of roasting and classic Heineken taste. This brew has delicious coffee notes and subtle sweetness.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
	(5981,2301,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/amstel-bottle.bmp\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2483\" alt=\"amstel bottle\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/amstel-bottle.bmp\" /></a>Amstel</h4>\r\n<h5>ABV:3.5%</h5>\r\nAmstel light is brewed with a unique mixture of barley and hops to create a light lager with full flavor. It appeals to import and craft beer drinkers on those occasions when they seek a refreshing, lower calorie beer- The Bier Drinker\'s Light.'),
	(5987,2297,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/strongbow.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2477\" alt=\"strongbow\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/strongbow.jpg\" width=\"55\" height=\"164\" /></a>Strongbow</h4>\r\n<h5>ABV: 5.3%</h5>\r\nStrongbow is a crisp, strong, dry premium imported cider from the U.K. which delivers maximum refreshment in an authentic, traditional English recipe. With its clean, strikingly refreshing taste and full body, Strongbow appeals to import beer drinkers everywhere.'),
	(5993,2291,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/buckler.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2482\" alt=\"buckler\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/buckler.jpg\" width=\"48\" height=\"165\" /></a>Buckler</h4>\r\n<h5>ABV: &lt;.05%</h5>\r\nMalty and smooth with a clean amber beer flavor, Buckler is brewed with the highest-quality, all natural ingredients that are the hallmark of Heineken. Start the evening with this non-alcoholic and you won’t want to switch.'),
	(10882,2210,'_mcb-blocks','a:1:{s:8:\"products\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"Products\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"editor\";}}'),
	(6243,2210,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/iclight-mango.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2403\" alt=\"iclight-mango\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/iclight-mango.png\" width=\"59\" height=\"165\" /></a>ICL Mango</h3>\r\nIC Light Mango is a tropical twist on the classic taste of IC Light. Mouth-watering natural mango flavors entice your senses to make a summer get-together feel like a tropical getaway. At only 95 calories, it’s the kind of vacation you can enjoy over and over again.\r\n\r\nabv : 3.8%'),
	(6654,2208,'_mcb-blocks','a:1:{s:8:\"products\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"Products\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"editor\";}}'),
	(6252,2208,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/iclight-berry.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2402\" alt=\"iclight-berry\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/iclight-berry.png\" width=\"59\" height=\"165\" /></a>IC Light Berry</h3>\r\nIC Light Berry is a bold remix of our classic IC Light taste – a crisp light beer with the tart sweetness of a perfectly balanced berry blend. Leave the ordinary behind and venture out into the wild and tasty side of life – Go Wild with IC Light Berry.\r\n\r\nabv : 3.8%'),
	(6416,2206,'_mcb-blocks','a:1:{s:8:\"products\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"Products\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"editor\";}}'),
	(6261,2206,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/iron-city-amber.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2401\" alt=\"iron-city-amber\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/iron-city-amber.png\" width=\"59\" height=\"165\" /></a>Iron City Amber</h3>\r\nIron City Amber is a super-premium amber lager with a deep copper color, sweet citrus aroma, and rich honey and caramel flavors. Specialty roasted malts blend with smooth, aromatic European hops for a crisp, well-balanced, and pleasantly drinkable beer.\r\n\r\nabv : 5.0%'),
	(10697,2204,'_mcb-blocks','a:1:{s:8:\"products\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"Products\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"editor\";}}'),
	(6270,2204,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/american.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2407\" alt=\"american\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/american.png\" width=\"58\" height=\"163\" /></a>American</h3>\r\nAmerican Beer is brewed tough to capture the spirit and strength of America. This lager’s crisp taste and bold packaging embodies patriotism and the same values our country was built on: pride, honor and dedication. Produced in 100% American made packaging and containing nothing but domestic ingredients, American is a proper beer for the hardworking everyman.\r\n\r\nabv : 4.7%'),
