	(7132,2169,'_mcb-products','[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Belgian_White_btl_clear_100x352_47_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2447\" alt=\"Shock_Top_Belgian_White_btl_clear_100x352_47_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Belgian_White_btl_clear_100x352_47_165.png\" width=\"47\" height=\"165\" /></a>Shock Top Belgian White</h3>\r\n<h5>BELGIAN STYLE WHITE OR WHEAT BEER</h5>\r\n<h5>YEAR ROUND</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 5.2%</h5>\r\nAt Shock Top Brewing Company they shake up traditional tastes with Shock Top Belgian White, a spiced Belgian-style wheat ale (\"wit\") brewed with real orange, lemon and lime peels. Then pair it with coriander spice to produce a crisp and distinctive taste with a satisfying flavor.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Honeycrisp_Apple_clear_100x351_47_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2446\" alt=\"Shock_Top_Honeycrisp_Apple_clear_100x351_47_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Honeycrisp_Apple_clear_100x351_47_165.png\" width=\"47\" height=\"165\" /></a>Shock Top Honeycrisp Apple Wheat</h3>\r\n<h5>FRUIT BEER</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 5.8%</h5>\r\nShock Top Honeycrisp Apple Wheat is a unique, hand crafted brewed hybrid of Belgian wheat beer and sweet cider, with natural Honeycrisp flavor added to produce an innovative new brew that is crisp, refreshing and flavorful.  This unfiltered brew is the perfect beer to welcome the warming Spring days.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Raspberry_Wheat_btl_clear_47_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2450\" alt=\"Shock_Top_Raspberry_Wheat_btl_clear_47_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Raspberry_Wheat_btl_clear_47_165.png\" width=\"47\" height=\"165\" /></a>Shock Top Raspberry Wheat</h3>\r\n<h5>BELGIAN STYLE WHEAT BEER</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 5.2%</h5>\r\nRaspberry Wheat delivers the same smooth taste of Shock Top, with a hint of raspberry flavor. This traditional Belgian-style wheat ale is brewed with essence of wild raspberry and hand-selected hops. It’s this combination that gives it its crisp and distinctive Shock Top taste, with its own flavorful twist. This unfiltered ale has a light-golden color and a smooth finish.\r\n<div>[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Pumpkin_Wheat_clear_100x340_49_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2449\" alt=\"Shock_Top_Pumpkin_Wheat_clear_100x340_49_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Pumpkin_Wheat_clear_100x340_49_165.png\" width=\"49\" height=\"165\" /></a>Shock Top Pumpkin Wheat</h3>\r\n<h5>PUMPKIN ALE</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 5.2%</h5>\r\nShock Top Pumpkin Wheat is a traditional Belgian-style wheat ale brewed with ripe pumpkins and a variety of autumnal spices, including nutmeg, cinnamon and cloves, for a refreshingly smooth beer that fully captures all the flavors of fall.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Lemon_Shandy_btl_clear_120x_47_165.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2448\" alt=\"Shock_Top_Lemon_Shandy_btl_clear_120x_47_165\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Shock_Top_Lemon_Shandy_btl_clear_120x_47_165.png\" width=\"47\" height=\"165\" /></a>Shock Top Lemon Shandy</h3>\r\n<h5>FRUIT/VEGETABLE BEER</h5>\r\n<h5>ABV: 4.2%</h5>\r\nShock Top Lemon Shandy is a unique interpretation of the classic Shandy. Brewed with two row and six row malted barley and five different types of hops, this Belgian-Style Wheat Ale is then combined with citrus peels, coriander, natural lemonade flavor and a hint of sugar for a subtle sweetness. The end result is an incredibly refreshing, crisp and smooth beer that hits the spot as the thermometer heats up.\r\n\r\n[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/shock_top_logo_B_100x.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2445\" alt=\"shock_top_logo_B_100x\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/shock_top_logo_B_100x.png\" width=\"100\" height=\"77\" /></a>Shock Top Sampler</h3>\r\n<h4>Summer</h4>\r\nHoney Crisp Apple Wheat\r\nBelgian White\r\nLemon Shandy\r\n\r\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\">[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]</span>\r\n<h4><span class=\"Apple-style-span\"><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/shock_top_logo_B_100x.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2445\" alt=\"shock_top_logo_B_100x\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/shock_top_logo_B_100x.png\" width=\"100\" height=\"77\" /></a>Fall</span></h4>\r\nBelgian White\r\nHoneycrisp Apple Wheat\r\nPumpkin Wheat\r\n\r\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\">[xt_divider style=\"shadow\"]</span>\r\n<h4><span class=\"Apple-style-span\"><a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/shock_top_logo_B_100x.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2445\" alt=\"shock_top_logo_B_100x\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/shock_top_logo_B_100x.png\" width=\"100\" height=\"77\" /></a>Winter</span></h4>\r\nBelgian White\r\nRaspberry Wheat\r\nChocolate Wheat\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>'),
