	(2487,1,'2013-11-04 13:41:56','2013-11-04 13:41:56','&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"width: 600px; margin: auto;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><!--more--></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">Mission Statement</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Be the best service sales, marketing and distributions system in our area- regardless of industry- setting a standard for all</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Provide the highest quality environment for all employees that is rewarding, challenging and stimulating</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Develop and reward teamwork which will maximize efficiency and productivity</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Constantly solicit and evaluate customer and employee feedback to refine and maximize internal and external satisfaction</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Project and maintain the highest quality image for our company and products</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"> <span style=\"color: #888888;\">Corporate Responsibility</span></h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/resp-matters.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2486\" alt=\"resp matters\" src=\"http://cfhq.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/resp-matters.jpg\" width=\"376\" height=\"134\" /></a>\r\n\r\nOur goal is to be the best beer company in a better world.\r\n\r\nA better world is a place where…\r\n<div>•<strong>Adults enjoy our beers responsibly.</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nFor more than 30 years, Anheuser-Busch has been the industry leader in promoting alcohol responsibility. Since 1982, when they launched their first responsible drinking campaign – Know When to Say When – Anheuser-Busch and wholesalers have invested more than $980 million in responsible drinking and the prevention of underage drinking and drunk driving.\r\n\r\n•<strong>We take action now to protect and preserve the environment.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nEnergy •Nearly 1 in 6 of A-B beers is brewed using alternative fuel including: Biogas, landfill gas, solar and wind.\r\n<div> Water •A-B reduced their water use by 40% over the last 5 years. Von\'s employees pledged to reduce water consumption.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Recycling •A-B recycles 99.6% of the solid waste in our breweries.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Partnerships •A-B support of organizations like Living Lands and Waters has helped remove more than 7 million pounds of trash from our nation’s rivers.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>•<strong>We strive to make a difference in the communities where we live and work.</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nCommunity outreach is at the core of Anheuser-Busch’s and Von\'s business philosophy.\r\n\r\nWe support programs and organizations that not only enrich the lives of individuals but make a positive and sustainable difference in our community.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">Directions</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our address is 675 Galleria Drive Ext., Johnstown, PA 15904</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Turn left into Home Depot, then stay left up the hill to our warehouse.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">[xt_gmap address=\"675 Galleria Dr Ext, Johnstown, PA ‎\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" full=\"yes\" marker=\"no\" scrollwheel=\"true\"]</p>\r\n\r\n</div>','                                                    About Us','','inherit','open','open','','1912-revision-v1','','','2013-11-04 13:41:56','2013-11-04 13:41:56','',1912,'http://cfhq.org/?p=2487',0,'revision','',0),
