	(2160,1,'2013-11-06 06:11:33','2013-11-06 06:11:33','<h3>Redhook</h3>\r\nRedhook Ales will quench the thirst of any craft beer drinker.  The original Redhook ales were modeled after spicy Belgian ales and today Redhook is known as one of the most technologically advanced craft brewers in North America.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><a href=\"http://redhook.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> </a></span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><a href=\"http://redhook.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Redhoo</a></span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><a href=\"http://redhook.com/\" target=\"_blank\">k Website</a></span></span>\r\n<h3>Widmer Brothers</h3>\r\nIn 1979 , having trouble finding beer in the U.S. that they liked to drink, brothers Kurt and Rob Widmer began making beer. After quitting their jobs in 1984, the Widmer brothers decide to turn their hobby into a vocation and open their own brewery.\r\n<h5><a href=\"http://widmerbrothers.com/beer/\" target=\"_blank\">Widmer Brothers Website</a></h5>\r\n<h3>Kona Brewing Company</h3>\r\nFather and son team Cameron Healy and Spoon Khalsa, had a dream to create fresh, local island brews made with spirit, passion and quality. They came to the Big Island to fulfill their vision.\r\n<h5><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><a href=\"http://konabrewingco.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Kona Brewing Company Website</a></span></h5>','Craft Brew Alliance','-','publish','closed','closed','','craft-brewer-alliance','','','2013-11-09 20:12:29','2013-11-09 20:12:29','',0,'http://cfhq.org/?post_type=project&#038;p=2160',0,'project','',0),
