	(2567,1,'2013-11-07 22:02:11','2013-11-07 22:02:11','<h3>O\'Doul\'s</h3>\nTogether, O\'Doul\'s and O\'Doul\'s Amber have won 13 consecutive awards in the non-alcoholic malt beverage category at the Great American Beer Festival dating back to 1993. They have also won 10 medals at the North American Beer Awards in the non-alcoholic malt-based beverage category and five World Beer Cup Awards in the non-alcoholic malt beverage category.\n<div></div>','A/B Non Alcoholic','-','inherit','open','open','','2132-autosave-v1','','','2013-11-07 22:02:11','2013-11-07 22:02:11','',2132,'http://cfhq.org/?p=2567',0,'revision','',0),
