	(2249,1,'2013-10-10 20:35:26','2013-10-10 20:35:26','One of our distinct classic beers brewed\r\nsince 1829, Yuengling Lord Chesterfield\r\nAle has as much rich heritage as it does\r\nflavor and appeal. Crafted in a unique\r\ntwo-stage European brewing style for\r\nenhanced bitterness, it utilizes both\r\nconventional kettle hopping and dry\r\nhopping after fermentation resulting\r\nin a dry sharp finish.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.yuengling.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Yuengling website</a>','Yuengling Lord Chesterfield Ale','.','publish','closed','closed','','yuengling-lord-chesterfield-ale','','','2013-11-08 21:43:40','2013-11-08 21:43:40','',0,'http://cfhq.org/?post_type=project&#038;p=2249',0,'project','',0),
